articles.title: Asian Athletics Championships 2023: India finish with 27 medals - Olympics
articles.description: Indian athletes, including Jyothi Yarraji and Parul Chaudhary, won 13 medals at the Asian Athletics Championships 2023 on Sunday to finish with 27 medals. Get results.
